âœ… Highly Scalable & Reliable â†’ Handles millions of messages per second.
âœ… Message Filtering â†’ Subscribers can filter messages based on attributes.
âœ… Event-Driven Architecture â†’ Works with AWS Lambda, Amazon SQS, and other AWS services.

